{"tid":401162,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"楊潤雄下週一至三訪京　蔡若蓮署任教育局長","createTime":"2017-09-15T11:38:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-15T17:17:47.000Z","uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"aeff05b321ba95da279c2562486a72e8e8141590","tid":401162,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T11:38:19.000Z","msg":"教育局局長楊潤雄將於下星期一（9月18日）傍晚啟程前往北京訪問，周三（9月20日）回港。期間由副局長蔡若蓮署任教育局局長，顯示蔡若蓮經歷喪子之痛後現已回到工作崗位。<br />\n<br />\n政府新聞稿指，楊潤雄訪京期間將會與中國教育部官員舉行會議，及禮節性拜訪國務院港澳事務辦公室及北京市教育委員會。他亦會於北京出席活動，與一批正在內地升讀大學的香港學生會面，了解他們的日常生活情況及需要。"},{"pid":"fd30ec780ace0093c9a43dfc7f8ec08eb645d74f","tid":401162,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T15:58:38.000Z","msg":"即刻推國民教育<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ab09ae6f600ffeabf79ae7da09d68b44f44868a","tid":401162,"uid":54371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T16:01:03.000Z","msg":"男人就升官、發達、死老婆<br />\n原來女人既版本係唔同<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08fb93e198ba5ec218a9cc72e01881d0217cd21a","tid":401162,"uid":6728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T17:17:47.000Z","msg":"蓮子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}